@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8080
@employeeUsername = chen_xu
@password = 123456

### 正常路径：员工登录
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{employeeUsername}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 正常路径：提交设备使用记录（注意：如果设备ID不为1，请自行替换）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/devices/1/logs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "purpose": "打印项目周报"
}

### 异常路径：向不存在的设备提交记录，预期 404
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/devices/999999/logs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "purpose": "打印项目周报"
}

### 异常路径：缺少 purpose，预期 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/devices/1/logs
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：请求体不是 JSON，预期 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/devices/1/logs
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "purpose": "打印项目周报"
  }
]

### 正常路径：员工登出
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：未登录提交设备使用记录，预期 401
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/devices/1/logs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "purpose": "打印项目周报"
}
